### Implementation Code

The Analytics component is implemented in `app/layout.tsx`:

```typescript
import { Analytics } from "@vercel/analytics/next";

export default function RootLayout({ children }) {
  return (
    <html lang="en">
      <body>
        <Navbar />
        <main>{children}</main>
        <Footer />
        <Analytics />
      </body>
    </html>
  );
}
```

This implementation follows the exact pattern from the official Vercel documentation for Next.js App Router projects.

### Next Steps for Deployment

To enable Web Analytics in production:
1. Deploy the application to Vercel
2. Enable Web Analytics in the Vercel dashboard under Project Settings → Analytics
3. Verify analytics data collection by checking the Network tab for requests to `/_vercel/insights`

### Conclusion

No code changes were required as Vercel Web Analytics was already properly installed and configured according to the latest official documentation. The implementation is correct and ready for production use.
